        <p class="hero-lede">
          Clipency helps brands activate distributed creator networks with campaign briefs, submissions, proof review, performance intelligence and payout visibility inside one focused operating layer.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="primary-btn magnetic">Launch a campaign</a>
          <a href="#system" class="secondary-btn magnetic">Explore the system</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-metrics">
          <div class="metric-tile">
            <strong data-count="4">0</strong>
            <span>Core workflow stages</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric-tile">
            <strong data-count="100">0</strong>
